+## Goal
+
+Execute the witness denial/error matrix omitted by 006Y8 and leave one acyclic owner for correction
+authority, projection, and write enforcement.
+
+## Depends On
+- 006Y8
+
+## Runtime Capabilities
+- `localhost-e2e-server`
